{"tid":578214,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港成為已發達經濟體中貧富懸殊最嚴重的地區","createTime":"2018-03-02T12:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T16:01:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25a5bb327bcb2b2e3ef6160171b18576624efd88","tid":578214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/基尼系数\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%9F%BA%E5%B0%BC%E7%B3%BB%E6%95%B0&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d9219b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/基尼系数</a><br />\n<br />\n香港成為已發達經濟體中貧富懸殊最嚴重的地區；即使把發展中經濟體包括在內，香港的貧富懸殊也十分嚴重，僅次於薩爾瓦多、哥倫比亞、智利、危地馬拉、巴西、南非以及一系列非洲經濟體而排名倒數18位[4]"},{"pid":"cc5c805936bbbe467316cbe628f37bcdd3860a08","tid":578214,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"正苦表示：關我撚事"},{"pid":"580f7bb29dbb93f1f2b5a6072d41fba8bce9f1fa","tid":578214,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"最但係排尾十<br />\n咁係咪最"},{"pid":"fae3a6ca6525731522e659b721fe0e58cd9dc337","tid":578214,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"同一筆錢對相對有錢人係好少錢無乜用， 但對相對貧窮既人就好多錢好好用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主張全民派錢， 唔係還富於富。"},{"pid":"e4744223723157a2a78fc32e2db218f9aba8a98c","tid":578214,"uid":9436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"580f7bb29dbb93f1f2b5a6072d41fba8bce9f1fa","tid":578214,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"最但係排尾十<br />\n咁係咪最"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"已發展經濟體中最嚴重<br />\n計埋發展中第十八<br />\n好難明？"},{"pid":"0c73a2699732266b8ba106ce70b18273ecf5227f","tid":578214,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e4744223723157a2a78fc32e2db218f9aba8a98c","tid":578214,"uid":9436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"580f7bb29dbb93f1f2b5a6072d41fba8bce9f1fa","tid":578214,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"最但係排尾十<br />\n咁係咪最"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"已發展經濟體中最嚴重<br />\n計埋發展中第十八<br />\n好難明？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"ok XD"},{"pid":"a915095eb7813c816ecc245556436dc0b2411431","tid":578214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fae3a6ca6525731522e659b721fe0e58cd9dc337","tid":578214,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"同一筆錢對相對有錢人係好少錢無乜用， 但對相對貧窮既人就好多錢好好用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主張全民派錢， 唔係還富於富。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82681112d4888a5570dff1fd06d826237cd4f598","tid":578214,"uid":140953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:03:37.000Z","msg":"上堂有聽過貧富懸殊唔代表d咩<br />\nA國可以50%人平均月入5萬，最top1%人月入100萬，最top0.01%人月入1萬<br />\nB國可以50%人平均月入1萬，最top1%人月入10萬，最top0.01.%人月入100萬<br />\n<br />\nA國貧富懸殊明顯嚴重好多，但實際上係富有好多<br />\n香港貧富懸殊嚴重只係有錢人太多<br />\n但普通人生活同月入其實同其他已發展地區冇太大分別<br />\n計埋稅同購買力，香港人人工同歐洲人比較算係最高，除左瑞士人<br />\n<br />\n不過依D當然只係理論層面<br />\n香港屋咁貴先係貧富懸殊既主因，而屋咁貴，其他野平都唔會抵消到個月入差距<br />\n結果香港人實際上比較窮"},{"pid":"548f109d52df3f3df0f8a803eb5f29f4e23e5fa6","tid":578214,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"調低貧窮線<br />\n貧窮問題已經解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dceb649434d75af01190abf400b0ba15b404959","tid":578214,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40cddd00c32a0824c21fdac22ea9b1aba55a3bdf","tid":578214,"uid":77222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"點嚴重完全睇唔到"}]}